column2: SELECT d.ra AS input_ra, d.dec AS input_dec, s.ra as s_ra, s.dec as s_dec, s.z as s_z, s.specObjID as s_specObjID, s.sciencePrimary, s.sdssPrimary, s.legacyPrimary, s.seguePrimary, s.segue1Primary, s.segue2Primary, s.bossPrimary, s.mjd AS s_mjd, s.survey, s.instrument, e.mjd AS e_mjd, e.specObjID as e_specObjID, g.specObjID as g_specObjID into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.CAGN_strict_radec AS d OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (d.ra, d.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON n.objid = s.bestObjID LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON s.specObjID = e.specObjID LEFT JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON s.specObjID = g.specObjID
